# CQ8.1 (COMPETENCY_QUESTIONS.md concept 8): "What is the current
# price-per-share, exchange ratio, earnout, and escrow percentage on the
# table?"
#
# Added in the 2026-07-18 L5-push Round 3 pass -- the first committed query
# to exercise Concept 8 (ma:DealTermLineItem), which only fixtures/case-2.ttl
# asserts (case.ttl and the mega-deal fixture do not touch this concept).
# Verified live against fixtures/case-2.ttl (2 rows:
# original-offer-price-per-share -> PricePerShare/42.50,
# original-offer-escrow -> EscrowPercentage/10.00) and confirmed 0 rows
# against fixtures/case.ttl (a real negative check: that fixture's own
# header discloses it does not exercise Concept 8) via the scratch consumer
# at /private/tmp/claude-501/-Users-sac-ggen/70ac08c7-8655-49c4-baa2-018bc441bb4c/
# scratchpad/l5-round3-ma-case-study-pack/.

PREFIX ma: <http://seanchatmangpt.github.io/packs/ma-case-study#>

SELECT ?term ?termType ?termValue WHERE {
  ?term a ma:DealTermLineItem ;
        ma:termType ?termType ;
        ma:termValue ?termValue .
}
